OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,FNigel Farage is facing questions about
OL,7,Fmoney he received from a crypto
OL,8,Fbillionaire just weeks before the 2024
OL,9,Fgeneral election.
OL,11,FLast year, Christopher Harborne gave
OL,12,FReform UK #9 million - the biggest
OL,13,Fdonation to a UK political party by a
OL,14,Fliving person. But it's a #5 million
OL,15,Fgift he gave to Nigel Farage two years
OL,16,Fago that has attracted the most
OL,17,Fscrutiny.
OL,19,FWhat is the story so far, and how big
OL,20,Fa problem could this be for the Reform
OL,21,FUK leader?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
