OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,FJust weeks after receiving the gift,
OL,7,FFarage purchased a house in Surrey for
OL,8,F#1.42 million. Sky News reported that
OL,9,Fthe house purchase was completed
OL,10,Fwithout a mortgage on May 10 2024.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Reform said: "The
OL,13,Frelevant chronology is
OL,14,Fstraightforward. The offer and
OL,15,Fpurchase process for the property
OL,16,Fcommenced before the gift.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779329020
OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,F"Mr Farage had already passed proof of
OL,7,Ffunds and the relevant checks before
OL,8,Freceiving the gift. The purchase was
OL,9,Ftherefore already proceeding
OL,10,Findependently of it."
OL,12,FHow was the house paid for?
OL,14,FLast week, Reform UK told the BBC the
OL,15,Fhouse was paid for using the fee Nigel
OL,16,FFarage received from appearing on I'm
OL,17,Fa Celebrity on ITV.
OL,19,FIn 2025, Farage told the Financial
OL,20,FTimes that the fee had been paid to
OL,21,Fhis company, Thorn In The Side Limited.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
