OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,FHowever, company accounts appear to
OL,7,Fshow the fee remained in the company
OL,8,Faccounts after the house purchase was
OL,9,Fcompleted.
