OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,FThe House of Commons code of conduct
OL,7,Fstates that "new Members must register
OL,8,Fall their current financial interests,
OL,9,Fand any registrable benefits (other
OL,10,Fthan earnings) received in the 12
OL,11,Fmonths before their election within
OL,12,Fone month of their election.
OL,14,FMPs found to have broken the rules
OL,15,Fcould be asked to apologise in the
OL,16,Fchamber, or face being suspended -
OL,17,Fwhich could eventually lead to a
OL,18,Frecall petition and by-election in the
OL,19,Fmost serious cases.
