OL,3,CWhy is Nigel Farage in trouble over #5
OL,4,Cmillion?
OL,6,FA spokesman for Reform UK said: "Mr
OL,7,FFarage's office is in communications
OL,8,Fwith the Parliamentary Commissioner
OL,9,Ffor Standards.
OL,11,F"He has always been clear that this
OL,12,Fwas a personal, unconditional gift and
OL,13,Fno rules were broken. We look forward
OL,14,Fto this being put to bed once and for
OL,15,Fall."
